MeMeShare 1.0
--------------------
MeMeShare is written on CodeIgniter framework and it supports most of the database systems. Check CodeIgniter site for more details.

Steps to setup MeMeShare:

1. After deploying on the server, go to application/config/ directory of the project to add the configuration for the database and the google O2Auth
2. Set the database connection details in the application/config/database.php
3. Set the google application credentials in the application/config/google.php
4. Run the SQL script found in setup/sql/ directory to create the database structure for the app in the database.
5. Go to the assets/img/ and replace the emailLogo.png, logo.png, productlogo.png with custom ones.
6. You should be set. Try browsing to the index page of the application.

Enjoy!

